==Mandarin==
[[Pinyin]]: dàmén bù chū, èr mén bù mài

===Etymology===
Literally: one neither goes outside of the front gate, nor strides toward the second (inner) gate.

===Idiom===
{{cmn-idiom|t|pin=dàmén bù chū, èr mén bù mài|pint=da4men2bu4chu1er4men2bu4mai4|tra=大門不出，二門不邁|sim=大门不出，二门不迈|rs=大00}}
# to never leave home, and have little contact with the outside world; to live a sheltered life

